{"arkId":"cl010115400","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010115400","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Statuette : Vierge \u00e0 l\u0027Enfant tr\u00f4nant","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Statuette : Vierge \u00e0 l\u0027Enfant tr\u00f4nant"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : gothique (Occident-\u003Emoyen \u00e2ge)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1200 - 1300","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1200,"endYear":1300,"imprecision":"","text":"XIIIe si\u00e8cle (?)","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Anonyme","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q4233718"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 10005","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"groupe d\u0027applique","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"La statuette, tr\u00e8s compacte, repr\u00e9sente la Vierge assise sur un si\u00e8ge moulur\u00e9. Elle est coiff\u00e9e d\u2019un voile court, simple, retenu par une couronne fleuronn\u00e9e, d\u2019un dessin large et \u00e9pais. Son visage est plein. Sa robe, serr\u00e9e \u00e0 la taille, s\u2019\u00e9panouit en plis en zigzags. Son manteau d\u00e9gage la taille, sur la gauche, tandis que, de fa\u00e7on tr\u00e8s inhabituelle, un pan passe sur l\u2019\u00e9paule gauche pour retomber derri\u00e8re l\u2019Enfant. Ce dernier, v\u00eatu d\u2019une longue robe qui laisse entrevoir ses pieds nus, b\u00e9nit de la main droite et tient une pomme dans la gauche. Le socle mince, \u00e0 pans coup\u00e9s, est taill\u00e9 en biais \u00e0 la base, ce qui entra\u00eene un d\u00e9s\u00e9quilibre du groupe vers la gauche. Le dos du groupe, lisse, indique qu\u2019il n\u2019\u00e9tait pas destin\u00e9 \u00e0 \u00eatre vu et que le groupe devait \u00eatre ins\u00e9r\u00e9 sous un dais ou dans un tabernacle.\r\nPolychromie moderne.","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"12,8","displayDimension":"12,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"6,5","displayDimension":"6,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"4,4","displayDimension":"4,4 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : ivoire d\u0027\u00e9l\u00e9phant = d\u00e9fense d\u0027\u00e9l\u00e9phant (ivoire tr\u00e8s sombre)\r\nTechnique : polychrome (techniques bambou\/ bois\/ corne\/ ivoire\/ \u00e9caille-\u003Epeint = peinture) (traces de polychromie)","placeOfCreation":"France (Europe) (?)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection Claudius C\u00f4te, Lyon ; legs Mme Marie-Fran\u00e7oise C\u00f4te, accept\u00e9 par d\u00e9cret du 9 juillet 1961","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Mme C\u00f4te, Marie-Fran\u00e7oise","note":"","role":", Donateur"},{"value":"M. C\u00f4te, Claudius","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"legs","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date du legs","value":"1961","startYear":1961,"endYear":1961},{"type":"date de comit\u00e9\/commission","value":"02\/02\/1961","startYear":1961,"endYear":1961},{"type":"date du conseil artistique des mus\u00e9es nationaux","value":"16\/02\/1961","startYear":1961,"endYear":1961},{"type":"date du d\u00e9cret","value":"09\/07\/1961","startYear":1961,"endYear":1961}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u00